            {
              "chord": "C",
              "lyrics": "granddaddy bad."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "lyrics": "Headed up the holler with everything he had."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "lyrics": "Before my time, but"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
              "lyrics": "I've been told."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "lyrics": "You never come back from Copperhead Road."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "lyrics": "Now daddy ran whisky in a big block Dodge."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": null,
              "lyrics": "Bought it at an auction at the Mason's Lodge."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": null,
              "lyrics": "Johnson County Sheriff painted on the side."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": null,
              "lyrics": "Just shot coat of primer, then he looked inside."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": null,
              "lyrics": "Well, him and my uncle tore that engine down."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": null,
              "lyrics": "I still remember that rumbling sound."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "lyrics": "Then the sheriff came around in the"
            },
            {
              "chord": "C",
