            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "lyrics": "Heard momma crying that something wasn't right."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "chunks": [
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "lyrics": "He was headed down to Knoxville with the"
